 ALONG All Ride alongs will be scheduled through the EMS Division Contact Ride along scheduling staff at 916 566 4000 What we need Your name Your phone number Date of ride along Time of ride along Ride along category EMT Student school affiliation CHP MICN Explorer or ROP
